    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine the effect of LCZ696 vs. Enalapril on improvement of
      excercise capacity in patients with chronic heart failure with reduced ejection fraction
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
